Board support layer for Meson

This layer currently provides support for the Overo series COMs 
produced my gumstix, available here:

https://www.gumstix.com/store/index.php?cPath=33

The majority of this metadata is derived from the official meta-gumstix layer 
available on github (git://github.com/gumstix/meta-gumstix.git). The key
difference is that this layer does not include any dependencies external
to poky. 


Dependencies
------------

Poky
  URI: git://git.yoctoproject.org/poky.git
  branch: denzil
  revision: HEAD

Maintenance
-----------

This layer is maintained by the Yocto Project. Send patches / pull requests
to yocto@yoctoproject.org with '[meta-meson]' in the subject.

